data.revised_prompt: Generate a professional, high-quality image of an 'Herbal Garden Fizz' cocktail. The cocktail is presented in a tall, sleek Collins glass. The drink's pale green color vibrantly shines through the clear glass, achieved by muddling fresh basil leaves. The gentle golden radiance of a lemon adds an extra aesthetic. Sparkling ice cubes magnify the refreshing aspect of the drink. The garnishing consists of a basil sprig and a twisted lemon strip intertwined and resting on the rim of the glass. Soft, natural light gently illuminates the cocktail, casting alluring reflections. The backdrop is a delicately blurred, lush garden projecting an aura of freshness and tranquility. The overall image composition stylishly portrays a calm, summery garden ambiance focusing on herbal and citrus elements. The cocktail recipie includes 2 oz Gin, 1 oz Elderflower Liqueur, 0.5 oz Lemon Juice, 4 Basil Leaves, topped with Club Soda. The image should look appeasing and photorealistic, akin to those captured by a professional food photographer. The background should be clear with a soft focus and devoid of any text or watermarks.
